---
import Container from "@/components/ui/Container.astro";
import Icon from "@/components/ui/Icon.astro";

const year = new Date().getFullYear();

const quickLinks = [
  { href: "/#hero", label: "Trang chủ" },
  { href: "/#solution", label: "Giải pháp AAC79 PLUS" },
  { href: "/kiem-dinh-cong-trinh/", label: "Kiểm định công trình" },
  { href: "/bang-gia/", label: "Bảng giá AAC79 PLUS" },
  { href: "/ho-so-nang-luc/", label: "Hồ sơ năng lực" },
];

const productLinks = ["Gạch E-Block", "Tấm E-Panel", "Sàn E-Floor", "Vữa & keo AAC"];
---

<footer id="footer" class="bg-ink-800 pt-16 pb-36">
  <Container>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-10 border-b border-white/8 pb-12 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-12">
      <div class="lg:col-span-5">
        <a href="/" class="inline-flex">
          <img src="/images/logo-aac79.png" alt="AAC79 PLUS" class="h-28 w-auto object-contain" />
        </a>
        <p class="mt-4 max-w-sm text-sm leading-relaxed text-white/55">
          Chuyên phân phối và thi công bê tông khí chưng áp (AAC) tại Khánh Hòa và khu vực Nam Trung Bộ. Giải pháp trọn gói – chất lượng tốt – đáng tin cậy.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="lg:col-span-2">
        <h5 class="mb-4 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-white/90">Menu nhanh</h5>
        <ul class="flex flex-col gap-2">
          {quickLinks.map((l) => (
            <li><a href={l.href} class="text-sm text-white/50 transition-colors hover:text-brand-accent">{l.label}</a></li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="lg:col-span-2">
        <h5 class="mb-4 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-white/90">Sản phẩm</h5>
        <ul class="flex flex-col gap-2">
          {productLinks.map((l) => (
            <li><a href="/#products" class="text-sm text-white/50 transition-colors hover:text-brand-accent">{l}</a></li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="lg:col-span-3">
        <h5 class="mb-4 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-white/90">Liên hệ</h5>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-2.5 text-sm text-white/50">
          <p class="flex items-start gap-2"><Icon name="headset" class="mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-brand-accent" />Tư vấn kỹ thuật: <a href="tel:0907523113" class="text-white/70 hover:text-brand-accent">0907 523 113</a> (Mr Hân)</p>
          <p class="flex items-start gap-2"><Icon name="shopping-cart" class="mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-brand-accent" />Đặt hàng: <a href="tel:0976228311" class="text-white/70 hover:text-brand-accent">0976 228 311</a> (Ms Đoan)</p>
          <p class="flex items-start gap-2"><Icon name="envelope" class="mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-brand-accent" /><a href="mailto:aac79plus@gmail.com" class="text-white/70 hover:text-brand-accent">aac79plus@gmail.com</a></p>
          <p class="flex items-start gap-2"><Icon name="globe-alt" class="mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-brand-accent" /><a href="https://aac79.com.vn" target="_blank" class="text-white/70 hover:text-brand-accent">aac79.com.vn</a></p>
          <p class="flex items-start gap-2"><Icon name="map-pin" class="mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-brand-accent" />Lô 20, đường 18A, KĐT Lê Hồng Phong II, Nha Trang</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-between gap-3 py-6 sm:flex-row">
      <p class="text-sm text-white/35">© {year} <a href="/" class="hover:text-brand-accent">Công ty TNHH AAC79 PLUS</a>. Bảo lưu mọi quyền.</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-white/35">Thiết kế bởi AAC79 PLUS · <a href="/#leadform" class="text-brand-accent hover:underline">Liên hệ ngay</a></p>
    </div>
  </Container>
</footer>
